<section class="commitment">

    <div class="container">

        <div class="commitment__content">

            <!-- image -->
            <div class="commitment__image-wrapper">

                <img
                    src="/photo_for_commitment.jpg"
                    alt="Supporting Indonesia's design community"
                    class="commitment__image"
                >

            </div>

            <!-- info -->
            <div class="commitment__info">

                <span class="commitment__subtitle">
                    Komitmen Kami
                </span>

                <h3 class="commitment__title">

                    Berkontribusi untuk

                    <span class="commitment__title-second">
                        Komunitas Desain
                    </span>

                </h3>

                <p class="commitment__text">
                    Woodara berkomitmen untuk mengalokasikan 10% dari keuntungan masa depan yang dihasilkan melalui proyek-proyek yang lahir dari kompetisi ini guna mendukung perkembangan ekosistem desain Indonesia.
                </p>

                <p class="commitment__text">
                    Dengan berpartisipasi dalam kompetisi ini, para desainer menjadi bagian dari misi yang lebih besar untuk memperkuat dan mengembangkan desain Indonesia bagi generasi mendatang.
                </p>

                <div class="commitment__tags">

                    <span class="commitment__tag">
                        Beasiswa Pendidikan
                    </span>

                    <span class="commitment__tag">
                        Workshop Desain
                    </span>

                    <span class="commitment__tag">
                        Dukungan Peralatan
                    </span>

                    <span class="commitment__tag">
                        Pelatihan Profesional
                    </span>

                    <span class="commitment__tag">
                        Eksposur Internasional
                    </span>

                    <span class="commitment__tag">
                        Dukungan Mahasiswa
                    </span>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</section>

<style> 

    .commitment {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 10rem 0;
    }

    .commitment .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 140rem;
        padding: 0 2rem;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .commitment__content {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 11rem;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .commitment__image-wrapper {
        aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    }

    .commitment__image {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        display: block;
    }

    .commitment__info {
        max-width: 64rem;
    }

    .commitment__subtitle {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        color: #111;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: 0.2rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 3.2rem;
    }

    .commitment__subtitle::before {
        content: "";
        display: inline-block;
        width: 0.6rem;
        height: 0.6rem;
        background-color: #111;
        border-radius: 50%;
        margin-right: 1rem;
    }

    .commitment__title {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        color: #111;
        font-size: clamp(4.2rem, 5vw, 5.4rem);
        font-weight: 300;
        line-height: 1.12;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        margin-bottom: 3.2rem;
    }

    .commitment__title-second {
        font-style: italic;
        color: #888;
        font-weight: 300;
    }

    .commitment__text {
        color: #888888;
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 2.4rem;
    }

    .commitment__text:last-of-type {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .commitment__tags {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 1.2rem;
        margin-top: 4rem;
    }

    .commitment__tag {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 1.2rem 2rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.1);
        color: #888888;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.14rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        transition:
            border-color 0.3s ease,
            color 0.3s ease,
            background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .commitment__tag:hover {
        border-color: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.2);
        color: #111;
        background-color: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.02);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {

        .commitment {
            padding: 5rem 0;
        }

        .commitment__content {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 3.5rem;
        }

        .commitment__subtitle {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .commitment__title {
            font-size: 3.2rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .commitment__text {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
        }

        .commitment__tags {
            gap: 0.8rem;
            margin-top: 2.4rem;
        }

        .commitment__tag {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1.4rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.1rem;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .commitment__tag:hover {
            border-color: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.1);
            color: #888888;
            background-color: transparent;
        }
    }

</style>